# OneCare Architecture

Full spec: `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`

## Layers

`Presentation → Application → Domain ← Infrastructure → Integrations (MCP)`

- Domain has zero imports from Nest, Prisma, Next, or OpenAI SDKs.
- Application orchestrates use cases via ports; Infrastructure implements ports (DI).
- Feature folders under `modules/<feature>/` with presentation | application | domain | infrastructure.
- Design each module so it can become a microservice later — no cross-feature table access.

## Patterns

Repository · DI · Domain events / outbox · Feature flags · Typed config (Zod)

## Prefer

Modular monolith first; extract workers/MCP servers at clear boundaries (`docs/ROADMAP.md`).
